data.description: NEW FLOORING- stunning home is the perfect combination of contemporary style and timeless charm! Enjoy gorgeous views from the many windows or the gorgeous covered decks of this 3 bedroom 2.5 bath home.  Situated on a .16 acre lot with access to the fenced yard from both floors and located in beautiful Grants Pass, this home is perfect for entertaining. With 1866 square feet of living space, this 2021 built home features many builder upgrades, an open floor plan, a leathered granite island and countertops, upgraded stainless steel appliances in the kitchen, a jacuzzi tub, and the primary bedroom on the main floor. Some of the contemporary extras include; an electric vehicle charger, motion activated outdoor lights, Remote controlled ceiling fans and wifi enabled appliances. The unique in-law floor plan offers plenty of privacy while still allowing everyone to stay connected with 2 bedrooms, a Jack and Jill bath, and a sitting area in the daylight basement.
